{"tid":2030820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】有無人諗過我地波台可以做Cheap and Dirty文宣？","createTime":"2020-05-23T04:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T11:34:18.000Z","uid":73381,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e1cde01aaf02c11891a46a8a0e84dc1641eab017","tid":2030820,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:21:57.000Z","msg":"既然香港依家處於唇齒存亡既時間<br />\n我地依班波台手足係咪可以做多啲野 為文宣同埋手足士氣出一分力？<br />\n因為我自己都整過唔同設計既文宣，考慮到我地時間唔多<br />\n我就諗緊可以整依種Cheap and Dirty既文宣<br />\n用自己影既相加個字落去 用咗我唔到兩分鐘既時間<br />\n叫人上下街 留意下發生緊既野<br />\n拋磚：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hoDSWBh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhoDSWBh.png&h=c4bf18a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SWCgDPG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSWCgDPG.png&h=fff9a84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為想大家盡快見到 所以我暫時整兩張先<br />\n<br />\n希望大家係下面都可以留低自己既作品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為波台手足為香港出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2762c869a85403f672ba11344fb343e644ffee5","tid":2030820,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"推下樓主介紹埋有咩app?"},{"pid":"ec1b23b41f811444a132662f959546db14d45f34","tid":2030820,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f2762c869a85403f672ba11344fb343e644ffee5","tid":2030820,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"推下樓主介紹埋有咩app?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"唔該晒手足<br />\n好問題 我一路都係用Photoshop黎整<br />\n不過考慮到可能有手足係無Photoshop<br />\n啱啱嗰兩張就用咗一個叫Adobe Spark既免費手機App黎整<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEBhhhq.png\"